<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Chris Brown and his girlfriend Brooke Meredith sparked rumours they had split earlier this year.</p>

<p>But on Friday, the pair put an end to the reports when they were spotted celebrating the veterinarian's 42nd birthday together in Sydney's eastern suburbs.</p>

<p>The couple appeared stony faced as they soaked up the warmer weather during a stroll. </p>

<p>Strolling in the sun: Dr Chris Brown (right) and his girlfriend Brooke Meredith (left) celebrated the veterinarian's 42nd birthday together when they were spotted out and about in Sydney's eastern suburbs </p>

<p>Chris cut a casual figure in a blue T-shirt and tan chinos which he paired with brown thongs. </p>

<p>The television presenter carried a grey puffer vest with him and shaded his eyes with a pair of trendy sunglasses. </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Brooke looked chic in a white collared shirt and a pair of denim jeans that flaunted a hint of her taut midriff.  </p>

<p>Style: Chris cut a casual figure in a blue T-shirt and tan chinos which he paired with brown thongs</p>

<p>The model accessorised the look with simple flats, a black crossbody bag and sunglasses. </p>

<p>She flaunted her stunning looks with natural makeup and wore her brunette locks in a half up 'do.  </p>

<p>The stroll comes after reports Chris had split from Brooke, after less than six months of dating.</p>

<p>Rumours: The stroll comes after reports that Chris had split from Brooke, after less than six months of dating</p>

<p>In August, Woman's Day claimed that Chris was back on the market after cryptically hinting at his split from the 29-year-old model on Instagram.</p>

<p>'Over the last few months there's been no more dependable partner in the pandemic than a face like this,' he wrote alongside a photo of his cat.</p>

<p>The couple were last spotted together back in May, when they were pictured holding hands during a romantic beach stroll.</p>

<p>Distance: Chris and Brooke (pictured) were last spotted together in May, when they were pictured holding hands during a romantic beach stroll</p>
